opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 24th day of September, 1996, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is Reserved pending the decision in Dynamic Student Services v. State System of Higher Education, 98 M.D. Appeal Docket 1995.
NEWMAN, J., did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
